{"tid":1059271,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"牙朗封神夜 世一摩在INS上為他瘋狂點贊!但網友扎心了","createTime":"2019-03-13T04:29:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T05:02:42.000Z","uid":25345,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"166691bfb8dc0a81fdec30a1d6e8337adf50cc74","tid":1059271,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T04:29:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/03/13/b5923a5c5e4d49edbd555bde754a7ce5.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcms-bucket.ws.126.net%2F2019%2F03%2F13%2Fb5923a5c5e4d49edbd555bde754a7ce5.jpeg&h=473b5a18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n牙朗時隔9個月又一次瘋狂戴帽，他的好友、皇馬金球先生莫德裡奇也在INS上點贊了8篇與牙朗有關的內容，去年莫德裡奇攬獎無數時，牙朗也曾私下發短信向其表示祝賀。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但皇馬卻恥辱性遭阿賈克斯逆轉無緣歐冠8強，有網友評價：&ldquo;馬德裡的兩支球隊均倒在了8強門外，一支是因為沒有了牙朗，另一支是因為有了牙朗。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"90f1ff8b1d8c819f043062fbd99039bf55c3e376","tid":1059271,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T04:32:19.000Z","msg":"牙朗真男人"},{"pid":"605f710c1c0ed73b22dd1add47f51c5a7c6f879d","tid":1059271,"uid":95,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T04:35:03.000Z","msg":"呀朗真係關鍵王"},{"pid":"c8b2cc264f8cc1da7e82f22f14962ac5c93aa410","tid":1059271,"uid":144466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T04:49:53.000Z","msg":"俾返個獎人啦"},{"pid":"2bcb54ccb7d3d9b2eba4c5a76c875c8dc44646ce","tid":1059271,"uid":25345,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T04:58:47.000Z","msg":"摩:比前面兩件廢野搞到我比人狂笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"627c891e54491d9dfc65c9fc70d53a695aac7525","tid":1059271,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T04:59:53.000Z","msg":"又對弱隊刷數據"},{"pid":"0c886b2797adb45511529f652e43b718027a6791","tid":1059271,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T05:00:05.000Z","msg":"唔計牙朗球十二球<br />\n兩球頂槌真係<img src=\"/assets/